io.lettuce.core.event

Interface EventBus

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEventBus

    public interface EventBus
    Interface for an EventBus. Events can be published over the bus that are delivered to the subscribers.

    3.4
    Author:
    Mark Paluch

        Flux<Event> get()
